{"tid":471032,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"大中小3款全面屏！三星Galaxy S9確切發布時間曝光","createTime":"2017-11-17T01:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T01:35:44.000Z","uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d0eee27b8dc00557c0132f2e165c09edaa1a9306","tid":471032,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"很多消息都指出，三星Galaxy S9將比較早的發布，也就是不會像GS8那樣，3月亮相4月開賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20171117/s_96f65c4c6d4e445199b15a95b7c98f32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20171117%2Fs_96f65c4c6d4e445199b15a95b7c98f32.jpg&h=32222459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此前，我們的猜測是1月的CES或者2月上旬單獨辦會，但似乎過於樂觀了。<br />\n據BGR引述India Today的報道，匿名消息人士透露，Galaxy S9將在MWC（世界移動通信大會）2018上發布。資料顯示，MWC 2018將於2月26日在西班牙巴塞羅納召開。<br />\n如果參考S7，那三星一般會提前正式開展一天，也就是西班牙當地時間2月25日。<br />\n報道還稱，雖然三星方面沒有對上述信息確認，但預計幾天內就會公開。<br />\n綜合目前的爆料，GS9預計有3款，其中S9和S9+屏幕大小和前作一致，但下巴極度收窄後，屏占比進一步拔升；同時，三星還准備了一款5寸屏4寸大小的S9 mini。<br />\n其他配置方面，首發驍龍845和Exynos 9810芯片，6GB RAM起步，增加類似iPhone X的3D人臉識別解鎖系統，後置1200萬+1600萬雙攝像頭，指紋也挪到了攝像頭下方，便於觸發。"},{"pid":"2c831817565bb6cbd186c5c14dae9bf5469583b8","tid":471032,"uid":5846,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"人用重直雙鏡佢又用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6ccc4907205db59d4110b95482dc705adb1f66","tid":471032,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"Mini 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ece3dc7d79365c4e6c81121316b9bba47eca467","tid":471032,"uid":152244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"小屏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f01d9d32bda